### What the tests cover

| Area | Tests |
|---|---|
| **Daily hours — lower bound** | Negative values rejected for every day |
| **Daily hours — upper bound** | Values > 24 rejected; exactly 24 accepted |
| **Daily hours — boundaries** | `0`, `0.5`, `8`, `12`, `23.5`, `24` all pass |
| **Weekly total — upper bound** | > 80 rejected; exactly 80 accepted |
| **Weekly total — lower bound** | 0 hours accepted |
| **Idempotency — no double save** | Retry with same key skips `save` |
| **Idempotency — stable result** | 10 retries all return identical payload |
| **Idempotency — key isolation** | Different keys → independent submissions |
| **Idempotency before validation** | Stored key bypasses re-validation |
| **Edge cases** | Fractional hours, empty entries, float overflow, auto-generated unique keys |

